1.We installed mongodb native so we can do operations like CRUD on our Database.
2.Then we installed mongoose so we don't have to write same boilerplate code 
 which we had todo in mongodb native.mongoose can do it for us.
 3.We installed bluebird as promise library because default promise library for
 mongoose is deprecated.
 4.We installed Body parser so that we can tak JSON anc convert to object 
 and send to our server.
 5.We installed Expect for assertion ,mocha for testing ,nodemon to execute 
 our program without refreshing and supertest to test our test the express routes.
6.We installed validator to validate Email. 
7.We installed crypto-js to hashing in playground.
8.Then JSONWebToken came for hashing.
9.Bcryptjs can be used for password hashing.